snippet.title: Quadrax gameplay (PC Game, 1994)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Quadrax, Dos PC game produced by Cauldron in 1994 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/quadrax/6083/
It is a game where two explorers pass different levels. It is a nice game worth trying.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
